                </a>
            </li>
            <li class="list-inline-item">
                <a title="Share via Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://www.kirkusreviews.com/book-reviews/janice-boland/a-dog-named-sam/&hashtags=kirkusreviews">
